CrossContractDependencies.TokenTransfer: Uses token.call to transfer tokens to the user address in WitdrawTokenToHolder and WithdrawToken, creating dependencies on external token contract behavior.
CrossContractDependencies.UncheckedLowLevelCalls: Relies on low-level calls for token and Ether transfers without verification of success.

InterContractConsistencyConditions.OwnerManagement: Consistency is needed to ensure that only the authorized owner makes withdrawals.
InterContractConsistencyConditions.TokenTransferSuccess: Low-level calls to external contracts should ensure consistent and verified behavior in successful transfers.
